<help olc tog_veh_stop>

If the path_cell is a stop, then make it not one.  If it wasn't, then make it one.  A
stop is where a vehicle automatically stops to let on and off passengers.

Syntax:  tog_veh_stop [vehicle_num] [path_cell_num]

Example:  tog_veh_stop 25 2         Toggle the second path cell.

<color=red>
See Also:  rstat, stat_path, ch_path_desc, set_path_dir, rem_path, add_path,
	   tog_veh_stop, list_paths
</color></help>
